name: Clog Boots black stars
description:
These galactic inspired clog boots from 'Noé and Zoë meets Tannhauser' will revive your child's look for the new season. The strong suede pair feature cool faded stars all over, with a non-slip sole and wooden mid-sole. Neon yellow on the inner-sole and at the back is finished off with nifty lace ties.

- Upper: Leather, Sole: Wood

PLEASE NOTE: Boots size small, we recommend to order one size up!

name: Clog Boots blue stars
description:
Dotted with trendy blue stars, these suede clog boots from 'Noé and Zoë meets Tannhauser' are guaranteed to bring their outfit to life. Featuring a sturdy wooden heel, a non-slip sole and bright neon yellow detail on the inner-sole and back, a lace tie at the top completes the stylish pair.

- Upper: Leather, Sole: Wood

PLEASE NOTE: Boots size small, we recommend to order one size up!

name: Clog Boots pink stars
description:
Patterned with pretty pink star print, these statement 'Noé and Zoë meets Tannhauser' clog boots will give your little girl’s ensemble that stylish boast. The tough leather pair feature lace ties at the back, neon yellow detail and a sturdy wooden mid-sole. Complete with a rubber non-slip sole, your little one will walk with confidence.

- Upper: Leather, Sole: Wood

PLEASE NOTE: Boots size small, we recommend to order one size up!
